s3-method.Rd

S3 methods to get and view internal data.

Usage

# S3 method for class 'igraph_ptr'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An igraph_ptr object.

...

Extra arguments passed to the method.

Value

The original x invisibly.

Examples

print(graph_tree(5L))
